Welcome to the 2023 Dutch Election Dashboard

NOTE: THE DASHBOARD MOVED! It has been adopted by the De Groene Amsterdammer (click here)!

This dashboard aggregates data from the Meta Ad Library to show how citizens are targeted during the 2023 Dutch parliamentary election.

If you want to know more about Who Targets Me and our work on ad transparency, visit us on whotargets.me!

This section shows total and daily spending of political parties in the run-up to the 2023 Dutch parliamentary election for the latest available data.
